<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>as far as the death penalty goes, there isnt enough of it, the punishment needs to match the crime, it needs to be swift and sure,thats whats wrong with our system, nothing is swift or sure, if you have a good lawyer or big bucks the punishment doesnt match the crime<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
